  "purpose" : "(Clinical Focus: Concepts which are used to identify a type of informational content that is relevant as an Advance Directive including the type of Advance Healthcare Directive document, and the appointment of healthcare agents, as well as other care experience preferences, treatment intervention preferences, health goals, and priorities.),(Data Element Scope: These concepts can be used as the range of answers to the question, what type of advance directives does this person have documented? Or individual concepts from this value set can be used to code the actual wishes of the patient for each of these areas where future planning preferences can be expressed.),(Inclusion Criteria: ),(Exclusion Criteria: )",
